---
title: "Final Fantasy XIV Shrine"
layout: layouts/ffBase.njk
customcss: "/assets/css/ffxiv/ffxiv-home.css"
permalink: /shrines/finalfantasyxiv/
intro: |
  <p>
    My soft little Eorzean corner ♡ A home for character progress, achievements, screenshots, future plans, and all the bits of FFXIV I love the most.
  </p>
---

<section class="ffxiv-home-page">
  <header class="ffxiv-home-hero">
    <div class="ffxiv-home-hero__card">
      <div class="ffxiv-home-hero__profile">
        {% if ffxivAchievements and ffxivAchievements.portrait %}
          <img
            src="{{ ffxivAchievements.portrait }}"
            alt="{{ ffxivAchievements.characterName or 'Violet Froggy' }}"
            class="ffxiv-home-portrait"
          >
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ffxiv-home-hero__info">
          <p class="ffxiv-home-kicker">✦ my warrior of light ✦</p>
          <h1>{{ ffxivAchievements.characterName or "Violet Froggy" }}</h1>
          <p class="ffxiv-home-world">{{ ffxivAchievements.world or "Phoenix · Light" }}</p>

          <p class="ffxiv-home-desc">
            I’ve been playing FFXIV regularly since 2019, and this little shrine is where I want to keep all my favourite bits together — achievements, housing plans, glamour ideas, gil goals, and memories from running around Eorzea.
          </p>

          <div class="ffxiv-home-links">
            <a href="https://eu.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/character/30338253/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lodestone ↗</a>
            <a href="https://www.lalachievements.com/char/30338253/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lalachievements ↗</a>
            <a href="/shrines/finalfantasyxiv/achievements/">Achievements Page ↗</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="ffxiv-home-stats">
    <article class="ffxiv-home-stat">
      <span class="ffxiv-home-stat__icon">⭐</span>
      <span class="ffxiv-home-stat__label">Achievement Points</span>
      <strong class="ffxiv-home-stat__value">{{ ffxivAchievements.achievementPoints or "—" }}</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="ffxiv-home-stat">
      <span class="ffxiv-home-stat__icon">🗺️</span>
      <span class="ffxiv-home-stat__label">Server</span>
      <strong class="ffxiv-home-stat__value">{{ ffxivAchievements.world or "Phantom [Chaos]" }}</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="ffxiv-home-stat">
      <span class="ffxiv-home-stat__icon">🕒</span>
      <span class="ffxiv-home-stat__label">Last Updated</span>
      <strong class="ffxiv-home-stat__value ffxiv-home-stat__value--small">
        {% if ffxivAchievements and ffxivAchievements.updatedAt %}
          <time datetime="{{ ffxivAchievements.updatedAt }}">{{ ffxivAchievements.updatedAt }}</time>
        {% else %}
          —
        {% endif %}
      </strong>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="ffxiv-home-grid">
    <article class="ffxiv-home-card">
      <h2>About My XIV Life</h2>
      <div class="ffxiv-home-copy">
        <p>
          My in-game name is <strong>Violet Froggy</strong>. I’m a bit of an altoholic and I love bouncing around different classes, roles, and little goals depending on what mood I’m in.
        </p>
        <p>
          Some of the parts of FFXIV I love most are the mix of cosy and chaotic things to do — one day I’m thinking about achievements or gilmaking, the next I’m messing around with crafting, gathering, housing, or glam plans.
        </p>
        <p>
          I also really like having long-term progress to chip away at, which is why I wanted this shrine to become a proper tracker over time instead of just a single static page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="ffxiv-home-card">
      <h2>My Favourite Bits</h2>
      <div class="ffxiv-interest-pills">
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Savage</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Ultimate</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Crafting</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Gathering</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Housing</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Decoration</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Achievements</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Gilmaking</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Alt Jobs</span>
        <span class="ffxiv-interest-pill">Long-term goals</span>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="ffxiv-home-card">
    <h2>Explore This Shrine</h2>
    <div class="ffxiv-home-navgrid">
      <a class="ffxiv-home-navcard" href="/shrines/finalfantasyxiv/achievements/">
        <span class="ffxiv-home-navcard__icon">⭐</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Achievements</h3>
          <p>My progress, recent unlocks, and what I might want to focus on next.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="ffxiv-home-navcard" href="/shrines/finalfantasyxiv/checklist/">
        <span class="ffxiv-home-navcard__icon">☑️</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Checklist</h3>
          <p>A little place for goals, grinds, and things I want to chip away at.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="ffxiv-home-navcard" href="/shrines/finalfantasyxiv/housing/">
        <span class="ffxiv-home-navcard__icon">🏡</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Housing</h3>
          <p>Decor ideas, inspiration, and house notes.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="ffxiv-home-navcard" href="/shrines/finalfantasyxiv/glams/">
        <span class="ffxiv-home-navcard__icon">👗</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Glams</h3>
          <p>Looks, outfit ideas, and glamour planning.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="ffxiv-home-navcard" href="/shrines/finalfantasyxiv/gil/">
        <span class="ffxiv-home-navcard__icon">💰</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Gil</h3>
          <p>Money goals, saving plans, and silly little gil dreams.</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ffxiv-home-card">
    <h2>Useful Links</h2>
    <div class="ffxiv-link-list">
      <a href="https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Official Final Fantasy XIV Website ↗</a>
      <a href="https://ffxiv.consolegameswiki.com/wiki/Final_Fantasy_XIV_Wiki" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FFXIV Wiki ↗</a>
      <a href="https://www.ffxiv-gathering.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FFXIV Gathering ↗</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ffxiv-home-card">
    <h2>Screenshots from Eorzea</h2>
    <p class="ffxiv-gallery-intro">
      A few little snapshots from my adventures, because no shrine feels complete without screenshots ♡
    </p>

    <div class="ffxiv-gallery">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/ff/gallery1.png" alt="FFXIV screenshot 1">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/ff/gallery2.jpg" alt="FFXIV screenshot 2">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/ff/gallery3.jpg" alt="FFXIV screenshot 3">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/ff/gallery4.jpg" alt="FFXIV screenshot 4">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/ff/gallery5.jpg" alt="FFXIV screenshot 5">
    </div>
  </section>
</section>